1
00:00:04,078 --> 00:00:11,216
My thinking at a particular stage 
was that

2
00:00:11,724 --> 00:00:14,527
the best thing I could do 
for anyone

3
00:00:14,677 --> 00:00:17,932
was to bring them to hear
from Srila Guru Maharaj.

4
00:00:18,112 --> 00:00:21,587
["We Are All Mahaprabhu's Men"]

5
00:00:21,587 --> 00:00:25,274
I thought, "If I do that, what more 
can I offer them than that,

6
00:00:25,274 --> 00:00:29,205
if I can somehow arrange that, 
bring them in connection with him—

7
00:00:29,697 --> 00:00:32,437
that'll be good for them, 
and I'll be there too,

8
00:00:32,437 --> 00:00:35,337
hearing what 
Guru Maharaj says and...

9
00:00:35,557 --> 00:00:41,927
So, with great confidence 
and joy, and verve,

10
00:00:41,927 --> 00:00:46,727
I would bring God-brothers 
and God-sisters

11
00:00:46,727 --> 00:00:49,527
to the lotus feet 
of Srila Guru Maharaj.

12
00:00:49,717 --> 00:00:53,330
And after bringing 
one such person...

13
00:00:57,690 --> 00:01:01,023
Srila Gurudev, he took us all,

14
00:01:01,023 --> 00:01:04,827
at the end of Guru Maharaja's talk
he took us all downstairs for a prasadam.

15
00:01:05,017 --> 00:01:09,067
And then the idea was after taking 
the prasadam to return to Mayapur.

16
00:01:10,255 --> 00:01:13,117
But at the end of the prasadam
Gurudev came to me and said,

17
00:01:13,117 --> 00:01:15,553
"Guru Maharaj wants 
to see you again."

18
00:01:18,643 --> 00:01:20,182
That was very unusual.

19
00:01:20,182 --> 00:01:23,433
So we went back upstairs, 
like three of us, four of us,

20
00:01:23,433 --> 00:01:24,634
to see Guru Maharaj.

21
00:01:24,634 --> 00:01:26,207
And Guru Maharaj said,

22
00:01:26,210 --> 00:01:33,760
"I was thinking your earnestness 
to serve Mahaprabhu is so great

23
00:01:34,070 --> 00:01:37,520
that He has personally 
supplied this prasadam.

24
00:01:37,860 --> 00:01:40,715
So I asked Govinda Maharaj 
to set some aside for me.

25
00:01:41,065 --> 00:01:43,090
I'm also taking that."

26
00:01:44,050 --> 00:01:46,007
That's how Guru Maharaj
was thinking.

27
00:01:47,491 --> 00:01:52,194
And then the one devotee went, "Oh...",
who was astonished, said,

28
00:01:52,477 --> 00:01:56,787
"Thank you! Thank you so much!"

29
00:01:57,422 --> 00:02:00,555
And Guru Maharaj was, 
"Thank you?"

30
00:02:01,030 --> 00:02:03,840
He said, "'Thank you', 
that doesn't sit well with me.

31
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:08,241
Because, he said, 
that presupposes two parties.

32
00:02:08,607 --> 00:02:11,445
And when one party... 
these two parties with separate 
interest,

33
00:02:11,445 --> 00:02:14,643
when one party gets 
something from the other party,

34
00:02:14,643 --> 00:02:16,962
they say, 'Thank you'."

35
00:02:17,469 --> 00:02:21,046
And then he turns and in a very 
affectionate way he said,

36
00:02:21,046 --> 00:02:24,010
"We are all Mahaprabhu's men."

37
00:02:26,186 --> 00:02:31,664
And I thought to myself, 
"He, who is so exalted,

38
00:02:31,664 --> 00:02:36,382
when he says 'we', 
he is including us."

39
00:02:36,552 --> 00:02:38,917
But there are people 
in our group,

40
00:02:38,917 --> 00:02:43,542
when they say "we", 
it does not include him.

41
00:02:43,852 --> 00:02:49,368
But he, who is so exalted, says, 
'We are all Mahaprabhu's men'."

42
00:02:49,737 --> 00:02:53,600
He is willing to include us in that.

